import React from 'react'; import './Picker.css'; /** * Picker component. */ class Picker extends React.Component { /** * * @param {props} props */ constructor(props) { super(props); this.date = new Date(); this.state = {date: this.date}; } /** * * @param {int} offset month to be incremented to */ changeMonth = (offset) => { if (offset === 0) { this.date = new Date(); } this.date.setMonth(this.date.getMonth() + offset); this.setState({date: this.date}); }; /** * @return {object} a
containing the picker */ render() { const months = ['January', 'February', 'March', 'April', 'May', 'June', 'July', 'August', 'September', 'October', 'November', 'December']; return (
this.changeMonth(-1)}> this.changeMonth(1)}>
this.changeMonth(0)}>{ months[this.state.date.getMonth()] + ' ' + this.state.date.getFullYear()}

); } } export default Picker;
